title: Microsoft Azure SQL Databases: Connections
agents: azure_v2
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the number of successful database connections
 as well as the rate of failed connections.

 The levels for this check can be configured using the ruleset
 "Azure SQL database connections".

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each database if all required metrics
 (average_connection_successful, average_connection_failed) are given.
